# Authentication Flow

This application uses Supabase for authentication. The authentication flow is handled through the following components:

- [src/app/auth](mdc:src/app/auth) - Authentication pages
- [src/components/auth](mdc:src/components/auth) - Auth-related components
- [src/middleware.ts](mdc:src/middleware.ts) - Authentication middleware
- [src/app/auth-handler](mdc:src/app/auth-handler) - Auth callback handlers

## Protected Routes

Routes under the following paths require authentication:
- `/dashboard` - Main dashboard
- `/clients` - Client management
- `/jobs` - Job management 
- `/reminders` - Reminders
- `/settings` - User and application settings

